createObject

protected Object createObject(COSBase kid)
Creates an object for a kid of this structure node. The type of object depends on the type of the kid. It can be
  • a PDStructureElement,
  • a PDAnnotation,
  • a PDXObject,
  • a PDMarkedContentReference
  • a Integer

Parameters:
kid - the kid
Returns:
the object
